        <item>
            <title>iOS 19 更多設計細節曝光，WWDC 2025 將發布近年最大更新</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/heres-another-look-at-the-glassy-ios-19-design-but-apple-has-bigger-plans/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=heres-another-look-at-the-glassy-ios-19-design-but-apple-has-bigger-plans</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/heres-another-look-at-the-glassy-ios-19-design-but-apple-has-bigger-plans/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:35:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299487</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 已正式公佈 WWDC 2025 將於 6 月 9 日至 13 日舉行，屆時將發布 iOS 19 等全新軟件平台。據傳，iOS 19 將迎來 Apple 歷史上最具規模的軟件更新。爆料者 Jon Prosser 近日分享了 iOS 19 的設計細節，展示其「玻璃風」視覺效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-4-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-4-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>Jon Prosser 最新影片透露了 iOS 19 的設計特色，採用「玻璃風、visionOS 主題」風格，涵蓋應用程式、按鈕及鍵盤等元素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-3-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-3-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-1-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-1-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-2-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-2-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>新設計強調圓潤美學與光澤感，界面邊緣彷彿從熒幕中「浮現」。鍵盤尤為突出，幾乎呈現懸浮效果，與 Apple Sports 及 Apple Invites 應用程式中的設計細節有相似之處。此外鎖定熒幕界面維持功能不變，但通知及按鈕增添半透明與 3D 浮動效果，設定選項及彈出式視窗亦採用更柔和的圓角設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-7-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-7-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>Jon Prosser 早前曾展示過 iOS 19 的相機及訊息應用程式模型，包含氣泡狀導航按鈕及更圓潤的界面元素。其補充指，目前曝光的版本未見主熒幕採用圓形應用圖標，但不排除未來調整可能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-5-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-5-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-6-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-6-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>而彭博社記者 Mark Gurman 則透露目前流傳的 iOS 19 圖像並非最終版本， Apple 還有更多計劃未曝光，6 月將有更多驚喜。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">iOS 19 images floating around aren&#8217;t representative of what we&#8217;ll see at WWDC. They look to be based on either very old builds or vague descriptions, missing key features. Expect more from Apple in June. Regardless, mockups &#8211; real or not &#8211; are always exciting for Apple watchers.</p><p>— Mark Gurman (@markgurman) <a href="https://twitter.com/markgurman/status/1904676788669690087?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 25, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>iOS 19 預計於 WWDC 2025 亮相後，隨即推出開發者測試版，公測版則於數週後發布，最終版本或於 2025 年 9 月或 10 月與新 iPhone 一同登場。業界預測，除視覺革新外，Apple 可能整合 Apple Intelligence 功能，如更智能的 Siri 或端到端加密 RCS 訊息。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_72054"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2RKrbTkP53M?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2025/03/25/ios-19-update-new-design-more-plans/">9to5mac</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
