        <item>
            <title>電動三輪車隊會展入閘惹爭議，港鐵：行動輔助裝置符合尺寸要求</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/electric-wheel-chair-in-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=electric-wheel-chair-in-mtr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/electric-wheel-chair-in-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:50:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電動輪椅]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299508</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日港鐵會展站出現一隊由 4 部三輪電動代步車組成的「車隊」，在職員協助下通過閘機出站，相關片段在網絡迅速流傳，引發熱議。港鐵回應指，涉事乘客為行動不便人士，所用設備符合港鐵尺寸要求。該些電動代步車被視為醫療用途的行動輔助工具，毋須根據《道路交通條例》領牌即可使用。消委會早於 2025 年 1 月建議，電動輪椅應符合國際安全標準並限速（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/consumer-concil-said-electric-wheelchair-rent-can-be-six-times/life-tech/health/">相關報道</a>），惟至今未見具體法例跟進。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="threadsdownloader.com_77946e" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1069500801?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲影片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>片段顯示，4 名人士駕駛款式相似的三輪電動代步車，在港鐵職員協助下有序通過闊閘機，其中一車旁掛有枴杖，有網友指或顯示使用者有行動困難。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250326_4_54_39-516x580.jpg" alt="" width="516" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250326_4_54_39-516x580.jpg 516w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250326_4_54_39.jpg 630w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 516px" /><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644921-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644921-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644921.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644907-437x580.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644907-437x580.jpg 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644907.jpg 678w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>有網民引用港鐵守則列明，輪椅及電動輪椅僅限行動不便人士使用，總重不得超 200 公斤，尺寸限制為 1200 毫米（長）× 700 毫米（闊），行駛速度應與步行相若（不高於時速 6 公里）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/485904571_1787723139-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/485904571_1787723139-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/485904571_1787723139.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>港鐵強調，職員當時協助有需要人士，同時維持車站秩序。據港鐵網站資料，持有殘疾人士登記證或醫生證明的人士，可使用符合規定的行動輔助設備。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644938-434x580.jpg" alt="" width="434" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644938-434x580.jpg 434w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644938.jpg 673w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 434px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644930-437x580.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644930-437x580.jpg 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644930.jpg 678w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>事件反映公眾對電動代步車使用的關注，隨着人口老化，行動輔助設備需求料增，政府或需加快制定清晰規管框架，平衡便利與安全。港鐵或會因應事件更新指引，減少誤解。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060310/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%8F%BE-%E4%B8%89%E8%BC%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A-%E6%83%B9%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E7%AC%A6%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-Juicy%E5%8F%AE?fbclid=IwY2xjawJQmeFleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHU3q2PCeVCkgznbaUVdfXxhJNk5-pjKZHEKeGR_mo2-5rsUnqzApSxdCKQ_aem_TxjEqFwRrS4rNmhhScUmSQ#goog_rewarded">星島</a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060310/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%8F%BE-%E4%B8%89%E8%BC%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A-%E6%83%B9%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E7%AC%A6%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-Juicy%E5%8F%AE?fbclid=IwY2xjawJQmeFleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHU3q2PCeVCkgznbaUVdfXxhJNk5-pjKZHEKeGR_mo2-5rsUnqzApSxdCKQ_aem_TxjEqFwRrS4rNmhhScUmSQ#goog_rewarded">Yahoo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
