        <item>
            <title>【教學】GPT 4o 文字 AI 繪圖大升級，圖中加字更準確 + 齋打字製作漫畫都得</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/gpt-4o-ai-graphic2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gpt-4o-ai-graphic2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/gpt-4o-ai-graphic2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:40:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4o]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299571</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在這個視覺當道年代，無論是社交媒體、簡報設計、還是創意創作，大家總會遇上一個煩惱：「我想畫圖，但我又不懂畫畫。」即使你腦海已有畫面，畫筆一到手卻不知從何下筆。這時候，ChatGPT 最新版本 —— GPT-4o 的圖片生成功能，便是一個幫到你實現「用嘴畫圖」的神隊友。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299540 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139-694x491.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="491" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139-694x491.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139.jpg 1273w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299541 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1-542x580.jpg" alt="" width="542" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1-542x580.jpg 542w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1.jpg 840w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 542px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299543 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709-609x580.jpg" alt="" width="609" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709-609x580.jpg 609w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709.jpg 946w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 609px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1.jpg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>這個功能讓任何人，只要用文字描述一下，就能立即生成圖片，甚至能自訂文字、角色表情、場景氛圍，連漫畫都畫得到！以下就以用户實際操作畫面與生成圖像作例子，帶大家一步步瞭解 GPT-4o 圖像生成功能的威力與使用方法。</p><p>ChatGPT 網址：<a href="https://www.chatgpt.com">https://www.chatgpt.com</a></p><p>Sora 網址：<a href="https://sora.com/">https://sora.com</a></p><p>*留意 ChatGPT, Sora 在香港需要透過 VPN 才可使用</p><h2>一、用文字畫圖？<b>GPT-4o </b>教你什麼叫「嘴畫力」</h2><p>GPT-4o 圖像生成功能的最大突破，是讓用户透過自然語言輸入描述即可生成圖片。從第一張圖片可見，用户只需輸入「請繪畫一張周潤發在街邊吃燒肉飯的圖片」，GPT 便成功生成一張笑容滿面的發哥，坐在露天街頭，手持叉燒飯開懷進食的畫面，背景還有唐樓與招牌，生活感十足。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1299527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="833" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1299528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="833" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></a></p><p>這種「精準圖像 + 角色情緒 + 明確動作」的輸出，可讓 GPT-4o 生成質素更高的相片。</p><p>使用方法：</p><ol><li>開啟 ChatGPT，選擇 GPT-4o 模式。點擊三點選項按鈕，選擇「建立圖像」；</li><li>在對話框直接輸入想像畫面，例如：「請繪畫一張周潤發很開心在街邊吃燒肉飯的圖片」。</li><li>若有指定角色表情、背景、物品，可直接列明，愈詳細愈精準。</li><li>約 30 秒內即會生成圖像。</li></ol><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299526 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-542x580.jpg" alt="" width="542" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-542x580.jpg 542w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247.jpg 840w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 542px" /></a></p><h2>二、可以加字的圖片！做梗圖、告白圖、創意海報無難度</h2><p>今次 GPT 4o AI 繪圖的更新，還令圖片內可更精準輸出中文字或英文字。雖然並非每一次都百分百準確，但你可多給它幾次機會，它也可製作出不錯的作品。</p><p>例如圖片中示範舉著寫有「我 ❤️ 黎明」紙牌站在紅磡體育館前，GPT-4o 除了能準確生成背景（紅館正門），還能將指定中文字體與紙牌內容準確呈現，整張圖極具真實感，仿如新聞照片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299530 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508-694x494.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="494" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508-694x494.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508.jpg 1263w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
